{"tid":513211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《溏心3》收視平平    司棋姐：好多人有自己渠道睇、偷睇、偷步，年輕人又會上網睇。","createTime":"2017-12-29T09:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T11:39:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":235,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"5d9a06aa83d6c7b931278a6b07a4cca9c5cad460","tid":513211,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171229/large/1514538702_e00c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171229%2Flarge%2F1514538702_e00c.jpg&h=1251e001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李司棋今日去商台接受訪問，提到左耳聽力問題：「我係突發性失聰，o依家戴左個助聽器，不過喺屋企就唔戴，所以我成日唔記得咗出門口戴番。個助聽器仲會播禪聲，可以訓練下隻耳。」佢話聽力問題無礙將來工作，問到司棋姐係咪真係拍《溏心風暴3》電影版？佢話要等夏雨搞，搞得掂會出聲，不過搞電影唔係咁容易，如果夏雨邀請佢拍都會參與。<br />\n<br />\n至於劇集收視平平，會唔會影響對電影版信心？司棋姐即刻為收視平反，指身邊好多朋友都有睇：「好多人有自己渠道睇、偷睇、偷步，年輕人又會上網睇。佢哋話已經睇到過咗30集，咁騰訊播多10幾集，香港收視實有影響，都要接受現實。」佢仲笑言好想上網「偷睇」，不過搵唔到渠道，唯有每晚錄低劇集重溫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/realtime/article/20171229/57640506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171229%2F57640506&d=PyvhatFNHvf0VQZCNupr9smB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=016da7ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171229%2F57640506&h=afb1aa30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/realtime/article/20171229/57640506</a>"},{"pid":"3348f575e98d9596731baa452daf1747d03bc223","tid":513211,"uid":389,"like":439,"dislike":8,"score":431,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:54:41.000Z","msg":"包括唔睇"},{"pid":"c03a816bb6f55ec4f8ba0dee08880aa95aaadc2f","tid":513211,"uid":8858,"like":248,"dislike":2,"score":246,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:57:59.000Z","msg":"啲老屎忽最鍾意搵藉口唔肯認失敗"},{"pid":"cc0ce968ebc8e2fa66e4f92a4d25a6